Packages that use thatslife 
Package Description
controllers  
thatslife  
  • Classes in thatslife used by controllers 
    Class Description
    ThatsLife
    That's Life (inspired by the board game "The Game of Life") This class is the master That's Life game class.
  • Classes in thatslife used by thatslife 
    Class Description
    ActionCard
    This class defines the ActionCard object.
    Card
    This Card class does not do anything but state the abstract method event.
    CareerCard
    This class defines the CareerCard, which inherits from the Card class.
    Deck
    This is the abstract superclass of all the card deck classes in the game.
    EndSpace
    This class defines the final space that players will land on, which is the retirement space.
    HouseCard
    This class holds the data for the houses in the game.
    MagentaSpace
    This class defines MagentaSpace, a type of space that requires the player to stop moving and execute its events.
    Map
    Main Map class.
    Path
    This class defines the structure blocks of the game, the paths.
    Player
    This is the Player class.
    SalaryCard
    This class contains the details about a player's salary.
    Space
    This class defines the very building-block of the game, the Space.
    StartSpace
    This class defines the StartSpace, the starting point (insertion point) of all players in the game.
    ThatsLife
    That's Life (inspired by the board game "The Game of Life") This class is the master That's Life game class.
    Transaction
    This class defines the structure for a transaction that will be done and recorded by each instance of player.
